      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA DONNA (7) steps out for the first time at this track. Scored in best time on card (34.60) latest winning by 1.1 lengths at The Meadows in a Grade 4/5. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Well placed and will be tough to beat. VISTA WEIRD (1) was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage third (34.72) at The Meadows. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expecting another good run. ELITE ONE (4) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten 1.5 lengths, (34.67) at Sandown. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Leading chance. LADY RAPID (2) has strong credentials from this draw.",
